# Heroicons Standard

- Use `@heroicons/react` for React icon usage in this project.
- Prefer `24/outline` icons unless a design specifically needs `24/solid`.
- Import icons by name (e.g. `InformationCircleIcon`) instead of inline SVG.
- Keep icon size and color controlled via Tailwind classes on the component.
- Do not add a second icon package unless explicitly requested.
